Real Images & Content"
Goal: Replace placeholders with real/realistic content

Tasks:
Task 1: Image Optimization System

Set up proper image handling:
- Create public/images folder structure
- Add high-quality placeholder images from Unsplash
- Optimize sizes (hero: 1920x1080, portfolio: 800x600, thumbnails: 400x300)
- Use next/image with proper sizes and quality settings

Task 2: Portfolio Content Structure

Enhance portfolio items:
- Add detailed descriptions
- Include project specs (materials, dimensions, year)
- Before/after shots if applicable
- Process photos
- Update lib/portfolio-data.ts with rich content

Task 3: Testimonials Section

Create components/sections/Testimonials.tsx:
- Carousel/slider of client testimonials
- Photos (or initials in circles)
- Star ratings
- Client name and project type
- Use shadcn Carousel component
- Autoplay with manual controls

Task 4: Stats/Numbers Section

Create components/sections/Stats.tsx:
- Reasonable numbers: "50+ Projects", "5+ Years", "98% Satisfaction"
- Counter animation on scroll into view
- Grid layout with icons
- Bronze accent colors
